data.title: Spring 2024 Dean's List Announced
data.meta_description: 1,989 students have been named to the Spring 2024 Dean's List at Kutztown University.
data.text:
KUTZTOWN, Pa. â€“ 1,990 students have been named to the Spring 2024 Dean's List at Kutztown University. To be eligible for the Dean's List, an undergraduate student must be registered for at least 12 credits and have a minimum grade point average of 3.60.

Students who have requested privacy (FERPA) have not been listed.

Click here to see the list in a pdf format.

Click here to view Kutztown University's Merit Page.
